# NOTE: gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar IS committed (intentionally).
# Without it `./gradlew` can't bootstrap on a fresh checkout — the jar
# is what reads gradle-wrapper.properties and downloads Gradle. Standard
# practice is to commit it.

